title: Vengeance Of The Gods: Viking Beach Landing - Total War: Attila Mod Gameplay
description:
Vengeance Of The Gods: Viking Beach Landing - Total War: Attila Mod Gameplay - Today we are going to see the God of Norse Mythology on the battlefield!  This is going to be a hilariously epic battle.  Thor, Odin, and Ullr lead their followers to glory in this Viking Beach Landing.  Utiplayer will be defending the beaches as the Saxons.  Enjoy the Battle :D

Mod Link: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=628013920&searchtext=

Utiplayer's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-72TRVjrj8EKBrZEg7sjFg

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
